Penguin Island is a
Small Island off the
coast of the City of
Rockingham

Its an animal
resserve which can
be reached by boat
or by walking, when

Penguin Island is one
of the few places in
the world where there
are penguins, Due to
their size (On ave,
33cm tall) they have
been dubbed as Fairy
Penguins.
